Allowing refugees to have better options rather than just three basic, impossible options like I said before and still benefits everyone
Overall we need a fresh perspective to increase options for refugees while recognizing that they do not have to be a burden on society
It is not a fixed rule that refugees become a cost
Yes, refugees are our humanitarian responsibility, but they are also human beings with skills, talents and aspirations who have the ability to contribute to society - if we allow them to
